data.description: Looking for a Home with Easy Access to Interstate 20 and Shopping?  Come Check this 3 Bed 2 Bath Stepless Ranch with a Full Basement located in Trails at Charleston Place in Villa Rica GA. This Home  Features a Basement with 12' Ceiling, Granite Counter Tops, Stainless Steel Appliances, New Roof, Levelled Backyard, Front Porch and  Back Deck, USDA Eligible, NO HOA, East Facing, 2 Car Garage.  There are not many Houses Available in this Market that have a Basement and this house is move-in ready!
